    <item>
      <title>农林中央金第二次投资失败之前曾有明确警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/norinchukin-s-second-investing-debacle-followed-clear-warning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本金融监管机构对农林中央银行的警告很明确——其对外国债券持有的深度依赖是一种危险的策略，需要改变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/norinchukin-s-second-investing-debacle-followed-clear-warning</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国家债务风险加剧，印尼债券市场受创程度居亚洲首位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/indonesia-s-bonds-hit-hardest-in-asia-as-state-debt-risks-grow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去两周，由于人们对印尼债务的担忧加剧，印尼国有电力公司的美元债券成为亚洲跌幅最大的债券。这给当地借款人带来了压力，他们面临 60 亿美元的债务到期日，预计到 2025 年底。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/indonesia-s-bonds-hit-hardest-in-asia-as-state-debt-risks-grow</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着指数日期临近，转向印度较长期债券的趋势延长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/switch-to-india-s-longer-dated-bonds-extends-as-index-date-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有迹象表明，在印度证券被纳入摩根大通指数之前，印度央行将坚持维持高利率，因此，印度的外国债券投资者正在锁定收益率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/switch-to-india-s-longer-dated-bonds-extends-as-index-date-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市即将下滑，日本就日元走势发出警告：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/asian-stocks-set-to-slip-into-cpi-election-week-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周亚洲股市将迎来通胀指标，这将有助于引导市场押注全球利率前景。日本最高货币官员加大干预力度后，日元保持稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/asian-stocks-set-to-slip-into-cpi-election-week-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 22:38:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保诚将回购价值 20 亿美元的保险公司自有股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/prudential-to-buy-back-2-billion-worth-of-insurer-s-own-shares</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保诚集团 (Prudential Plc) 启动了一项 20 亿美元的股票回购计划，该计划将不迟于 2026 年中期完成，该保险公司概述了相关进展，其中包括向股东进一步提供现金回报的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/prudential-to-buy-back-2-billion-worth-of-insurer-s-own-shares</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 22:25:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行达成协议，让澳大利亚现金快递公司维持运营</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/banks-strike-deal-to-keep-australia-cash-courier-firm-afloat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚的大型银行和杂货商同意向陷入困境的现金运输公司 Linfox Armaguard Pty Ltd. 注资 5000 万澳元（3300 万美元），此举旨在维持纸币和硬币在经济中的流通。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/banks-strike-deal-to-keep-australia-cash-courier-firm-afloat</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 21:49:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国开发商佳兆业重返法庭接受清算听证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/chinese-developer-kaisa-returns-to-court-for-liquidation-hearing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[很少有中国开发商像佳兆业集团控股有限公司一样，象征着解决房地产债务危机的漫长道路，该公司将于周一在香港一家法院避免被清算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/chinese-developer-kaisa-returns-to-court-for-liquidation-hearing</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚养老金规模达 1170 亿美元 引发更多房地产动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/australia-pension-with-117-billion-hunts-more-property-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚第三大养老基金，规模 1,750 亿澳元（1,170 亿美元）的 Aware Super，正在寻找全球房地产资产，希望在本周结束的财年取得强劲的投资业绩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/australia-pension-with-117-billion-hunts-more-property-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本散户投资者关注日元干预的风险押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-22/japan-s-retail-investors-eye-risky-wagers-on-yen-intervention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于日元下跌增加了日本再次干预市场的可能性，大批散户交易员似乎正在重新押注日元反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-22/japan-s-retail-investors-eye-risky-wagers-on-yen-intervention</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
